  <section class="section">
    <div class="lede">
      <div class="lede-head">
        <p class="section-num">§ I</p>
        <h2>What it is</h2>
      </div>
      <p>A repository overlay for Claude Code. It sets the rules Claude follows in this codebase, in this session, with the hooks that enforce them at the tool boundary. Memory, prompts, and skills are helpful. Hooks are load-bearing.</p>
    </div>

