  <section class="section">
    <div class="lede">
      <div class="lede-head">
        <p class="section-num">§ II</p>
        <h2>Why hooks</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Hooks run outside Claude's tool boundary. When a hook blocks a tool call, Claude never executes it. The dashed lines below are the surfaces Claude cannot reach. Memory is helpful, prompts are helpful, hooks are load-bearing.</p>
    </div>
