      <figcaption><strong>The tool boundary.</strong> Hooks fire at the dashed lines. Three of those events are guarded enough to make consent unforgeable: the consent_gate_grant hook on UserPromptSubmit writes the marker; the corresponding PreToolUse guard validates it before allowing the approval-token write.</figcaption>
