      <div class="arch-col worker">
        <span class="label">Isolated worktree</span>
        <h3>Where execution runs</h3>
        <p>The single subagent (<code>swarm-worker</code>) executes a fully-specified recipe. No design choices, no scope expansion, no test edits.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Skill(scenario)</li>
          <li>Skill(implement)</li>
